== Ravana ==


'''Ravana''' lonkecho raza ani valmiki ramainnacho kholpurux. pulos'tio rixichea vixrova nanvachea putacho ho put. ramainnant hache avoichem nanv koiksi oxem sanglam. punn kexini ani puxpotkotta oxinch tichim nanvam mellttat. avoi vonxakoddlean raun rakxos ani bapai vonxakoddlean to brahmnn axil'lo. tacho bapui ognihotri ani topsompon'n axil'lo. tori ravnnak avoi vollonn lagil'lem. to tea kallant mohabllixtt axil'lo ani tachekodden xurta, huxarkai, chikatti, nirbhoita ani svabhiman he gunn zoxe asle toxem modandhokai, duxttkai sarkil'le durgunnoi asle. kumbhokornn ani bibhixonn oxem taka don bhav ani xurponnokha hi bhoinn axil'li. mondodri hi tachi pott'ttoranni. indrojit, devontak, norantk, trixiros ani ontikai he put axil'le. ravnnak dha tonddam ani vis hat axil'leachem kainkodden vornnon melltta. tachevelean taka doxnan hem nanv poddlam asumie. valmikin taka don hat ani don tondd axil'leachem sanglam. tori valmikiramainnant kainkodde tacho doxgriv oso ul'lekh asa. kuber ho tacho savotr bhav. tachekodden bhorpur aspot ani puxkoll viman axil'lem. ek dis to vimanant bosun bapaiak mellpak vota astana ravonnache avoin taka polloilo. tika motsor zalo, tinnem ravnnak kuberavori xrimont zanvk sanglem. ten'na ravnnak gokonnak vochun dha hozar vorsam topochxrarea keli. dog ek hozar vorsachea nimannem brohmadevan prosn'n zavn monxakoddlean tuka mornnacho bhoimi na oso vor dilo, oxi tache sombondi kotha asa.

hea vora uprant to anikui bollixtt zalo. lonka hi kuberachi rajdhani axil'li. ravonnan addangiponnan ticher zoit melloilem. hachebhair tannem morut't, onronnio hea adi zaitea razank haroile. indr adi devankoi tannem haroile. patollacher zoit mellovpak gel'lekodden bollin tacho porabhov kelo. karotvoi-i orzunan taka dhonnuche dorien bandun dovoril'lo. pulosteache sangnnen tachi suttka zali. donddkarnneat tannem sadhurup ghevn sitek ubarun vheli. tannem sitek vox korpak zaite upai kele. punn sita taka vox zali na. nimannem ramakodde zal'lea zhuzant taka moronn ailem.

ramainnant ravonnachea gunn durgunnavixim mhaiti melltta te promann to iachkank dan ditalo, tacher ovlombun axil'leank palloditalo. toxench to vhodd totvgineani ani dhorm'- kormachea achoronnant ogorgonnio axil'lo. punn hea sogllea gunnancher mat korpi durgunn tachekodden axil'lo. takalagun tachekodde axil'lea ginnancho borea kamakhatir upeg zalo na. kaim ramainnant addvad mhonntta toxem ravonnachem udat'tikoronn korpacho iotn zala aslo, tori valmikiramainnant taka ek kholpurux mhonnunoch chodd chitravop zala. lok mansantoi tachi protima chodd promannant gholltta.





